project_descr: To support government  to increase capacity and stimulate other actors to find innovative and sustainable solutions to health system challenges and provide management support and technical assistance for the health program in Indonesia.

outputs.output_descr: Increased government capacity on health policy development of procurement and supply chain management to escalate accessibility and affordability on prevention and health care treatment for low-income and vulnerable groups
Institutional strengthening government and non-government on management and technical matter to ensuring quality of programme implementation.
